TypingGame in C++

Objective: to build a typing game that uses a keyboard device for input and to train finger mechanics such as speed, accuracy, and precision.

User inputs text
   check if true/false
Read block text
     kept on heap
Load new data (next game)

GUI display:
-start/exit
-user input
-timer
-displays current wpm
-displays text
          *support for basic text & unique-drawn text (own graphics)

Text processing:
-read in a file
      *convert to basic text-input handling (ASCII)
               Unique font displays incorrect characters
-put all characters 
                                                                      
               
    